hh3cMultilinkPPP.name: hh3cMultilinkPPP
hh3cMultilinkPPP.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cMultilinkPPP.description: The HH3C-MP-MIB provides read access to MP(Multilink PPP) link status information. The information available through this MIB includes: the father channel, the bundled son channel, the slot on which MP bundled, the number of son channels, the bundle name, the statistic of lost fragments, reordered packets, unassigned packets, interleaved packets, and the received/sent sequence, etc.

hh3cMpMultilinkTable.name: hh3cMpMultilinkTable
hh3cMpMultilinkTable.description: This table describes the information of MP link. The index of this table is the interface index of MP group or VT(Virtual Template).

hh3cMpMultilinkEntry.name: hh3cMpMultilinkEntry
hh3cMpMultilinkEntry.description: Each entry in this table describes the information of MP link. The available information includes: the father channel, the slot on which MP bundled, the number of bundled son channels, the statistics of lost fragments, reordered packets, unassigned packets, interleaved packets, and received/sent sequence.

hh3cMpMultilinkDescr.name: hh3cMpMultilinkDescr
hh3cMpMultilinkDescr.description: The interface name of the father interface on which MP bundled. It is the name of a Virtual Temblate or a MP group.

hh3cMpBundleName.name: hh3cMpBundleName
hh3cMpBundleName.description: The bundle name of the multilink. when authentication is configured, the bundle name is the authenticated user name; when authentication not configured, the bundle name is multilink.

hh3cMpBundledSlot.name: hh3cMpBundledSlot
hh3cMpBundledSlot.description: The slot on which MP bundled.

hh3cMpBundledMemberCnt.name: hh3cMpBundledMemberCnt
hh3cMpBundledMemberCnt.description: The number of the bundled son channel of the MP link.

hh3cMpLostFragments.name: hh3cMpLostFragments
hh3cMpLostFragments.description: The number of fragments of the MP link discarded because bad fragments received, or assembling packet failed, etc.

hh3cMpReorderedPkts.name: hh3cMpReorderedPkts
hh3cMpReorderedPkts.description: The number of received packets of the MP link reordered.

hh3cMpUnassignedPkts.name: hh3cMpUnassignedPkts
hh3cMpUnassignedPkts.description: The number of received packets of the MP link waiting for reordering.

hh3cMpInterleavedPkts.name: hh3cMpInterleavedPkts
hh3cMpInterleavedPkts.description: The number of received packets of the MP link interleaved by the packets queued in RTPQ(Real-time Transport Protocol Queue) or LLQ(Low Latency Queue).

hh3cMpRcvdSequence.name: hh3cMpRcvdSequence
hh3cMpRcvdSequence.description: The current sequence number of the MP link for receiving.

hh3cMpSentSequence.name: hh3cMpSentSequence
hh3cMpSentSequence.description: The current sequence number of the MP link for sending.

hh3cMpMemberlinkTable.name: hh3cMpMemberlinkTable
hh3cMpMemberlinkTable.description: This table describes the information of son channels of the MP link. The index of this table is the interface index of MP group or VT(Virtual Template).

hh3cMpMemberlinkEntry.name: hh3cMpMemberlinkEntry
hh3cMpMemberlinkEntry.description: Each entry in this table describes the information of the bundled son channels of MP link. The available information includes: the interface index of the son channel, the interface name of the son channel.

hh3cMpMemberlinkSeqNumber.name: hh3cMpMemberlinkSeqNumber
hh3cMpMemberlinkSeqNumber.description: The bundled sequence number of the son channels of the MP link. This object is one of the index of the table.

hh3cMpMemberlinkIfIndex.name: hh3cMpMemberlinkIfIndex
hh3cMpMemberlinkIfIndex.description: The interface index of the son channels of the MP link.

hh3cMpMemberlinkDescr.name: hh3cMpMemberlinkDescr
hh3cMpMemberlinkDescr.description: The interface name of the son channels of the MP link.

hh3cMpMemberlinkMpStatus.name: hh3cMpMemberlinkMpStatus
hh3cMpMemberlinkMpStatus.description: The MP status of the son channels of the MP link.

hh3cMpCompliance.name: hh3cMpCompliance
hh3cMpCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the H3C Multilink PPP MIB.

hh3cMpMandatoryGroup.name: hh3cMpMandatoryGroup
hh3cMpMandatoryGroup.description: A collection of objects providing mandatory MP information.

hh3cMpInfoGroup.name: hh3cMpInfoGroup
hh3cMpInfoGroup.description: All running information of MP feature.
